{"tid":1486133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有人想19/8塞鐵","createTime":"2019-08-18T18:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T19:12:31.000Z","uid":182802,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"16982c3578bcd703f5e65be379776ae338629e2c","tid":1486133,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:45:34.000Z","msg":"塞鐵撚聽日又發起塞鐵，話要響應港鐵車長行動<br />\n我唔支持咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日本身係車長就住自身安全問題罷工，而家走去塞鐵等同騎劫左人地<br />\n<br />\n而且聽日罷工帶黎嘅不便本身係大條道理入狗同港鐵數，但塞一塞所有野又會入番我地數，可以點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxFRnKF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxFRnKF.png&h=200f6175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcBdA4K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcBdA4K.png&h=5b3f4709&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6b258459d18f37b695e760163e9c96cadb43b11","tid":1486133,"uid":152209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"塞鐵作用唔大 加人香港人奴性極重"},{"pid":"abf8a32c8f98244907e7d9f806d3330cc959787e","tid":1486133,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:47:25.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要說「推」，試著說「８２３人鏈」<br />\n<br />\n８２３人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486119</a>"},{"pid":"520a64c316c78c8609f46b10bff06779bc57c189","tid":1486133,"uid":2300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:48:55.000Z","msg":"你地搞不合作<br />\n車長罷工行動會失焦<br />\n政府一定會賴晒班示威者令到港鐵班次受影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342d1f234f1776be3d3fc744b58e8737241e4f0d","tid":1486133,"uid":174283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cited